Telkom has launched its Big Deal for July 2019. This deal allows users to sign up to 10Mbps Uncapped Fibre for R649 per month on a 24-month contract. The following is included in the July 2019 Big Deal: The Netflix voucher covers July, August, and September – meaning you will only begin (or resume) paying for your Netflix subscription from October 2019. This Big Deal is only available to users who are in an area that is covered by Openserve, and is subject to Telkom’s dynamic Fair Usage Policy. The deal is available to new customers, DSL customers migrating to fibre, and customers upgrading to higher speed bundles. <span data-mce-type="bookmark" style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; overflow: hidden; line-height: 0;" class="mce_SELRES_start">﻿</span>